          "Modern LED landscape fixtures offer precise color temperature control, typically in the 2700K to 3000K range that produces the warm, inviting glow most homeowners prefer. Higher color temperatures (4000K+) are available for commercial and security applications where brighter, cooler light is appropriate. Dimmable LED drivers allow adjustable brightness levels that can change the mood of an outdoor space from bright entertaining to quiet relaxation with a single app command.",
